description	"Imperial Navy Trooper

^2Weaponry:
- E-11D Blaster Carbine [EE-4] (2)
- Blaster Pistol (2)
- 1 Pulse Grenade

^8Attributes:
- Heal (1)
- Reinforcements (1)

Imperial Navy troopers were soldiers in the Galactic Empire who were assigned by the Imperial Navy as part of Imperial Fleet Regiments to serve as guards and soldiers onboard its many Star Destroyers and other installations, such as the Death Star."
